data.description: UPDATED PHOTOS!!!  Nestled in the heart of the picturesque Kissimmee, this exquisite 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom, 2-story home offers an unparalleled living experience. With its prime location by the serene shores of Lake Toho and a thoughtful design that blends modern comfort with timeless elegance, this property presents an exceptional opportunity for those seeking a luxurious and relaxing lifestyle.  Key Features:  Spacious Elegance: Boasting a generous 3,512 square feet of living space, this home provides ample room for family gatherings and entertaining friends.  If fishing is what you love to do, use the neighborhood boat lift to travel over to Lake Toho. Modern Design: The open-concept layout effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting space filled with natural light and a seamless flow.  Gourmet Kitchen: The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious island that serves as the heart of the home.  Private Primary Suite: The main floor offers a luxurious primary suite that provides a peaceful retreat, complete with a spa-like en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet.  Comfortable Upstairs: Ascend the gracefully designed staircase to discover four additional bedrooms, providing ample space for family members or guests, along with two full bathrooms for added convenience.  Outdoor Oasis: Enjoy the Florida lifestyle to the fullest in the privacy of your fenced backyard, ideal for hosting barbecues, picnics, or simply basking in the sun.  Convenient 2-Car Garage: The attached 2-car garage ensures secure parking and additional storage space.  With its idyllic location, spacious interiors, and modern amenities, this exceptional property is a true gem. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a place to entertain loved ones, this 5-bedroom home offers a lifestyle that's both elegant and relaxing. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of Kissimmee's finest living.
